The paper also deals with large-scale data, which suggests that it may belong to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the paper mentions experiments on three large choice datasets, which suggests that it may also belong to the Electronic Commerce (cs.EC) sub-category.
